NAME

    Claws Mail NewMail plugin

DESCRIPTION

    Write a msg header summary to a log file (defaults to ~/Mail/NewLog)
    an arrival of new mail *after* sorting

    Every entry looks like:

    ---
    Date:   Fri, 23 Sep 2005 09:41:47 +0200 (METDST)
    Subject:        New Mail Plugin for SC
    From:   sender@host.somehwere.net
    To:     r.e.cipient@here.com
    Cc:     claws-mail-users <claws-mail-users@lists.sourceforge.net>
    Size:   17204
    Path:   /home/merijn/.sylpheed-gtk2/tempfolder/processing/1
    Message:        1
    Folder: (null)

